                <h1>Inventions Excluded from Digital Communications Background</h1>
                <p>When exploring the background of digital communications, inventions like the telegraph, telephone, and fiber optics are often highlighted. However, one invention that is not included is the mechanical typewriter, as it primarily pertains to text input rather than the transmission of digital signals.</p>
